quran[31]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,43,"(Pakwanga) chachitiji: “Nganituŵa mwa akuswali.”"
  74,44,"“Soni nganituŵa nkwaaliisya masikini.”"
  74,45,"“Ni twaliji nkutiŵila (mu sambi) pamo ni akutiŵila.”"
  75,40,"Ana Jwalakwe (Allah jwaŵapakombwele kutenda yele) nganaŵa jwanti ni kombola kwasyusya (ŵandu) ŵawe?"
  77,31,"Nganiuŵa mwa m'bulili wachisisimila soni wangakamuchisya kwilamba (lya Moto).”"
  77,32,"Chisimu Walakwe (Motowo) ukasaponyaga (pakutatasika) ndamba (syekulungwa) mpela nyumba jandalaja."
  77,33,"Syanti mpela ngamiya syam'bilichila."
  78,28,"Ni ŵaikaaniile imanyilo Yetu naikanilape."
  78,29,"Soni chindu chilichose tuchisunjile paachilemba m’Chitabu."
  78,30,"Basi pasyani; mwanti ngatun'jonjechesya (inepe) ikaŵeje ilagasyo (pachanya pa ilagasyo)."
  79,22,"Kaneka jwachitundumalile (chikulupi) aku junankulimbichila (kwasiŵilila ŵandu kwa Allah)."
  79,23,"Basi jwaasonganganyisye (asaŵi) nikwaŵilanga (ŵandu)."
  79,24,"Ni jwatite: “Une ni nam'mbuje gwenu jwapenani kusyene!”"
  80,19,"Kuumila m’mesi (gaŵalume ni ŵakongwe) an'gumbile, ni kumpanjila mpango (wakagumbidwe kakwe)."
  80,20,"Kaneka naakun'jepepachisyaga litala (lyakopochela ku duniya)."
  80,21,"Kaneko nakasampaga chiwa ni kunsiika m’malembe."
  81,16,"(Ni) syasikwendaga (chilo kaneka) ni kusisika pakutiŵila."
  81,17,"Ni nguchilumbila soni chilo ndema jachikwika ni kutyoka."
  81,18,"Ni ngukulumbila soni kumasikusiku ndema jakukulanguka."
  82,10,"Soni chisimu kwa jenumanja kwana (Achimalaika) ŵakunnolela (ni kusunga itendo yenu). ",footnotes:1:[Akusimulila Abȗ Hurairah رضى الله عنه yanti: Ntenga jwa Allah ﷺ jwatite: “Achimalaika akupisyanganaga pakwika kukwenu chilo ni muusi. Ni akusimanganaga wosope pa swala ja Fajr ni pa swala ja Asr. Kaneka aŵala ŵatemi namwe chilo chosope ni akasakwelaga (kwa Allah), ni akwawusyaga kutendaga Jwalakwe ni Jwakumanyilila nnope kwapunda ŵanganyao: “Achikapolo ŵangu mwalesile uli?” Basi ŵanganyao ni akasatiji pakwanga: “Twalesile achiswaliji, nambo soni twaasimene achiswaliji.” (Swahîh Al-Bukhârî, Hadith No. 530).]
  82,11,"Ŵakuchimbichika, ŵakulemba."
  82,12,"Akumanyilila yankuntenda."
  83,7,"Yakuona! Chisimu yakulembedwa ya (masengo ga) ŵandu ŵakusakasya nnope ili mu Sijjin."
  83,8,"Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Sijjin?"
  83,9,"Chele ni chitabu (chekulungwa) chachilembedwe (nkati mwakwe yakusakalape)."
  84,4,"Ni kwisa kuponya kusa (litakalyo) yayaliji nkati mwakwe nikuŵa mwangali chachipali."
  84,5,"Ni kwisa kunda lilamusi lya M’mbujeegwe, soni liichiŵajilwa (kuti likunde)."
  84,6,"E mmwe amundu! Chisimutu mmwe nkukangamala wa kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) nchilimbichilaga (kutenda itendo yambone kapena yakusakala), basi ni tinchisimangana nayo (pa lisiku lya Kiyamalyo)."
  85,1,"Ngulilumbila liwunde lyalikwete ndondwa syekulungwa-kulungwa ni mwakwenda mwakwe."
  85,2,"Ni Lisiku Lyeŵichidwe chilanga."
  85,3,"Kwisa soni nkuŵichila ni nkuŵichilidwa umboni."